<p>Inayaili is a web designer based in Belfast. She works for <a href="http://www.canonical.com/">Canonical</a> (the company that delivers Ubuntu). She writes articles on her blog, <a href="http://webdesignernotebook.com/">Web Designer Notebook</a>, on subjects such as CSS, HTML and web design. Inayaili is a frequent contributor to <a href="http://www.smashingmagazine.com/">Smashing Magazine</a> and <a href="http://24ways.org/">24 Ways</a> and she is the author of <i>Pro CSS for High Traffic Websites</i>. Surprisingly, she loves naps.</p><p>Inayaili has <a href="http://yaili.com/">an online portfolio</a> and tweets as <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/yaili">@yaili</a>.</p>